1. *Osveta* je slatka kada se dugo čeka. (Revenge is sweet when it's long awaited.)
2. Planira da izvrši *osvetu* nad svojim neprijateljem. (He plans to take revenge on his enemy.)
3. Traži *osvetu* za nepravdu koju mu je nanio. (He seeks revenge for the injustice that was done to him.)
4. Njegova *osveta* je bila surova i krvava. (His revenge was brutal and bloody.)
5. Ona je odlučila da neće tražiti *osvetu* već oprost. (She decided not to seek revenge but forgiveness.)
6. *Osveta* nije pravo rešenje, treba pokušati razgovorom rešiti problem. (Revenge is not the right solution, one should try to solve the problem through dialogue.)
7. Mnogi ljudi smatraju da je *osveta* greh. (Many people believe that revenge is a sin.)
8. *Osveta* nije uvek slatka, može ostaviti gorak ukus u ustima. (Revenge is not always sweet, it can leave a bitter taste in the mouth.)
9. Njegova *osveta* je bila tako suptilna da nije ni primetio šta se dogodilo. (His revenge was so subtle that he didn't even notice what happened.)
10. Njihov rat traje već godinama i niko ne želi da popusti jer žele *osvetu*. (Their war has been going on for years and no one wants to back down because they want revenge.)